Na '''iSoqosoqo veivukei''' e dua na veivukei soli ka vakavuli ni marama ena The Church of Jesus Christ of Latter-day Saints (Church YDE). A tauyavutaki ena [[1842]] mai Nauvoo, [[Illinois]], [[Amerika]], ka sa rauta e 7.1 million na lewe ni [[Lotu]] ena kena 188 na vanua kei na yasana. E dau vakatokai vakalevu na iSoqosoqo Veivukei ki na Lotu kei ira tale eso me vaka na "e dua vei ira na mataisoqosoqo makawa ka levu duadua ni marama e vuravura."

